sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Frontend
  participant Kong
  participant Service as Domain Service
  participant MongoDB
  participant RabbitMQ
  participant Analytics

  User->>Frontend: Action (browse/publish/subscribe)
  Frontend->>Kong: HTTP request
  Kong->>Service: Routed request (plugins applied)
  Service->>MongoDB: Read/Write
  Service->>RabbitMQ: Publish event (optional)
  RabbitMQ->>Analytics: Consume event
  Analytics->>MongoDB: Update aggregates
  Service-->>Kong: Response
  Kong-->>Frontend: Response
  Frontend-->>User: UI update
